	<Title>
		The power of positive thinking
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;Negative thoughts can feed pessimism and create unnecessary stress. You can learn to turn negative thoughts into positive ones. The process is straightforward, although it&apos;s challenging, especially at first. Start by following one simple rule: Don&apos;t say anything to yourself that you wouldn&apos;t say to anyone else. Throughout the day, stop and evaluate what you&apos;re thinking. If a negative thought enters your mind, evaluate it rationally and respond with affirmations of what is good about yourself&lt;/p&gt;
